<div class="hero">
  <br />
  <div class="frosty col-10 offset-1 text-center">
    <br />
    <h1>Seriously hungry plants</h1>
    <br />
    <h2>Meet ups in your local area</h2>
    <br />
    <h2>Resources for the help you need</h2>
    <% if user_signed_in? %>
      <br />
      <h2>Feel free to explore!</h2>
      <br /><br />
    <% else %>
      <br />
      <%= link_to 'Join our community', new_user_registration_path , class: 'btn btn-success' %>
      <br /><br />
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>

<br />
<div class="row feature text-center">
  <div class="col-12 col-sm">
    <h3>Amazing Community</h3>
    <br />
    <p>Find the help you need to raise your little carnivores. Wether you are just starting out or are a pro you are sure to find something helpful here.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="col-12 col-sm">
    <h3>Find local stores</h3>
    <br />
    <p>It's always hard to find local places that sell carnivorous plants. It is always best if you can inspect the product yourself before purchasing. Our community made database of local Texas stores helps direct you to where you need to go.</p>
    <%= will_paginate @shops %>
    <% @shops.each do |shop| %>
      <div class="booyah-box col-10 offset-1">
        <h1><%= link_to shop.name, shop_path(shop) %></h1><br />
        <i><%= shop.address %></i><br /><br />
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <div class="col-12 col-sm">
    <h3>Growing tips blog</h3>
    <br />
    <p>Being in Texas you know it is hotter here than most places. Our blog is full f tips to help deal with the heat and keep your little carnivores not only alive but thriving. </p>
  </div>
</div>
